*Umrli* su se okupili na groblju. (The dead have gathered at the graveyard.)
Učesnici su *umrla* počastili minutom ćutanja. (The participants honored the deceased with a minute of silence.)
*Umrlog* je rodjak postavio spomenik. (A relative of the deceased erected a monument.)
Niko nije znao koliko je *umrlih* bilo. (Nobody knew how many had died.)
*Umrlima* su se održale sahrane. (Funerals were held for the dead.)